	omen	talking	I am currently investigating that possibility.
	player	teasing	Tell me your findings.	Player_bench_hehe
	omen	surprised	Sure. And listen to this: even after my continued attempts to murder him, he hasn't tried to imprison me; instead, he has been taking care of me.
	omen	surprised	He even has me, the one plotting his demise, living with him!
	omen	angry	All because he insists he wants to "be with me as I go through the first steps of my redemption".	O_stupidredemption
	omen	grumpy	Something must be very wrong with him.
	player	lookingdown	Well, Omen... hearing all that, I'd say something must be very right with him.
	omen	disgust	Hmph... nonsense.	Oex_disgust
	player	teasing	I'd even say that you, with your unrivaled wits and unparalleled perceptiveness, have been capable of seeing how much he cares for you.
	omen	default	...
	omen	blush	...Well, I guess he's not THAT terrible.
	omen	rage	BUT IF YOU EVER TELL HIM I SAID THAT I WILL CLAW YOUR ORGANS OUT OF YOUR BODY.	Oex_rage
	player	animesweat	Hehe... duly noted.
	narrator		You two keep talking about the "torment" that is living with Liam.	
	narrator		Apparently Omen loves his cooking, although she phrases that sentiment quite differently, of course.

>>>	cdate_omen_2
>event_type	conversational
>conversational_type	stage1
>conversational_npc	omen
>action			Being a volunteer at Spooky Con
>layout	duo	omen,player
