	omen	confident	How could we not? I am the commander of our army of friends, while he is the second-most essential piece: an incredible morale booster.	Oex_confident
	omen	surprised	Still, it is honestly baffling how someone who wears the skull of a dead warrior as his face could be that soft!
	omen	confident	An enigma of a person, if you ask me. But nonetheless, he is priceless in his ability to encourage and inspire everyone who surrounds him.
