	omen	grumpy	Look at Doug, for instance: he might be excellent at giving hugs, but he has zero combat skills!
	omen	surprised	Or Zoe: an admirable woman of incredible might that has rejected destruction to embrace... what? Happiness?	O_justwhy
	player	lookingdown	You make them sound really swell, actually.
	omen	disgust	Hmph... then, there's Nico: a mimic who won't shapeshift.
	player	thinking	Well, yes, they rarely do it.	Player_bench_yeah
