>>>	cdate_doug_1
>event_type	conversational
>conversational_type	stage1
>conversational_npc	doug
>action			Family
>layout	duo	doug,player
	doug	happy	I love my family.	DOU_awwwhappy
	doug	distracted	Dad is a bit harsh, and I sometimes get nervous that he might not understand my life choices...
	doug	bliss	...but Mom is my forever champion. She always supports me no matter what.
	player	default	Aw, that sounds super sweet.	Player_bench_nice
	doug	bashful	Yeah!
	doug	blush	Like, for instance, Dad wasn't super on board when I adopted this look.
	doug	sad	He's a bit old school, so he didn't get why I didn't want to be a cube.
	player	surprised	Oh, you used to be a cube?	
	doug	distracted	I was. It wasn't so long ago that slimes started exploring shapes other than blob or cube.
	doug	explaining2	It takes some practice and preparation, but eventually you can adopt a different form.	DOUex_default
	doug	sad	Dad was perplexed. He said slimes oughta be cubes because it's an excellent shape to adapt to the halls of dungeons.
	doug	shocked	Which led to a 2-in-1 upset of me telling him I don't intend to work as an enemy to beat in a dungeon.
	player	teasing	Daaaaang, Doug the rebel! I didn't have you pinned for a bad boy.
	doug	bashful	Hehe, Doug the bad boy, that's me!
	doug	surprised	But nah, I was shaking like a jelly on a plate. It's not that Dad was mad or anything, but he was sort of befuddled!
	doug	explaining1	And that's when Mom came to the rescue. She's a sort of expert translator: she understood me instantly, and then put it in words Dad could understand too.
	player	lookingdown	She sounds like a wonderful woman.
	doug	happy	She totally is, %CURRENTPLAYERNAME%.	DOUex_happy
	player	blush	And hey, Doug... of course I'd love you in any shape you had...
	player	affirming	...but I gotta say this one shape is a good one.	Player_bench_nice
	doug	hyped	Right? I love it! It's great for hugs!
	narrator		You ask Doug to give you a test hug to confirm it. He's not wrong!	

>>>	cdate_doug_2
