	player	smilinginlove	Ha! I 100% know, Doug.	Player_bench_hehe
	doug	explaining1	Yup! So April and I started hanging out, talking about anime and playing lots of video games.
	doug	surprised	She'd always wipe the floor with me. She's way more competitive than you'd think!	DOU_whoa
	doug	happy	Always losing would've been a bit of a bummer if it wasn't for her coming up with the funniest bits and jokes while playing.	
